{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, RegulonDB confirms the transcriptional interaction between TF CRP-cyclic-AMP and its target genes deoC, deoA, deoB, and deoD, from 16 sources.",
    "Similarly, interactions confirmed from a higher number of experimental and/or analytical sources will have a higher CF e a e t and thus, are more likely to be true.",
    "A threshold value (CF e a e t = γ) is defined, and all regulations with CF e a e t <γ are treated as false positive.",
    "The final output of the framework will be a set of highly confident extracted entity pairs and their corresponding CF e a e t values, representing the accuracy of the retrieved relationships.",
    "We first describe the experimental setup, including the hyperparameter configuration and evaluation metrics used."
  ]
}